WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.000
Oh, the emperor doesn't know anything?

2
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:04.220
Although the empress can't go out

3
00:00:04.240 --> 00:00:07.320
But asked the guards to help spread the news saying oh

4
00:00:07.320 --> 00:00:09.280
Lenggong sells all kinds of snacks.

5
00:00:09.280 --> 00:00:13.200
Maybe those popsicle smoothies the Empress used to make were so delicious

6
00:00:13.200 --> 00:00:16.740
Good guy, after everyone heard it, they went to the cold palace to buy it one after another?

7
00:00:17.480 --> 00:00:22.240
Even the Empress Dowager asked Mammy Li to go to the cold palace to buy a lot of food and drink at night

8
00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:25.540
Forbidden clan still dares to do business in the palace

9
00:00:25.640 --> 00:00:27.460
I really thought I wouldn't punish him

10
00:00:27.560 --> 00:00:30.480
The emperor has beaten you since you banned people

11
00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:32.460
I haven't slept well for several nights

12
00:00:32.760 --> 00:00:34.700
He said he would punish people again.

13
00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:36.820
It's not you who are uncomfortable

14
00:00:37.080 --> 00:00:38.140
Pardon me?

15
00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:42.480
Ouch, what's wrong with the emperor?

16
00:00:42.480 --> 00:00:43.900
Are you in a bad mood?

17
00:00:44.040 --> 00:00:46.560
It's okay, why did the Empress Dowager come suddenly?

18
00:00:46.560 --> 00:00:47.720
Hot weather

19
00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:49.160
It gets cooler in the evening.

20
00:00:49.160 --> 00:00:51.020
Come out for a walk

21
00:00:51.240 --> 00:00:54.640
I just asked Mammy Li to go to the cold palace and buy some iced juice.

22
00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:56.740
Would the emperor like to have a taste?

23
00:00:56.840 --> 00:00:58.340
I don't drink that stuff

24
00:00:58.400 --> 00:01:01.320
I look at the emperor's impatient appearance

25
00:01:01.320 --> 00:01:02.700
Is on fire

26
00:01:03.120 --> 00:01:06.100
Why don't I buy you two popsicles and come back to eat?

